<lb ed="B" n="0632b19"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0632b20"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="11"><cb:jhead>大覺普濟玉林禪師語錄卷之十一終</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>